{
  "lines": [
    {
      "key": "18.0",
      "line_index": 18,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "65167af2",
      "speaker": "イビリア",
      "ja": "パ～パ♥　パ～～パっ♥　いっぱい甘やかしてぇ～♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "21.0",
      "line_index": 21,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "480a09c8",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "──イビリアっ！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "24.0",
      "line_index": 24,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ef321466",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "突然甘えモード全開で部屋にやってきたイビリア。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "25.0",
      "line_index": 25,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b9378325",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "部屋に入ってくるなり、俺に抱きつき催促するように",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "25.2",
      "line_index": 25,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "b9378325",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "頭をスリスリと胸に押し付ける。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "28.0",
      "line_index": 28,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d1622442",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "離れなさい、昨日も甘えたんだから今日はお預けだから",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "33.0",
      "line_index": 33,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "fdd0147d",
      "speaker": "イビリア",
      "ja": "やんや～っ♥　いっぱいバブバブしゅるのっ♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "33.2",
      "line_index": 33,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "fdd0147d",
      "speaker": "イビリア",
      "ja": "してくれないとや～なのぉっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "36.0",
      "line_index": 36,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "29e102e1",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "あ……待って！　泣くなって……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "39.0",
      "line_index": 39,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "59e6f1d1",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "イビリアは俺に拒絶されたと勘違いをし、瞳に大粒の涙をためる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "40.0",
      "line_index": 40,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "103628d1",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "どうにかなだめようとイビリアの頭をナデナデするが、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "40.2",
      "line_index": 40,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "103628d1",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "効果が薄く、とうとう泣き出してしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "44.0",
      "line_index": 44,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4a250c1c",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（今日はいつにも増して甘えっぷりがすごいな……。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "44.2",
      "line_index": 44,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "4a250c1c",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ストレスが限界に達してしまったんだろうか……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "48.0",
      "line_index": 48,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7e3b755b",
      "speaker": "イビリア",
      "ja": "パ～パ！　パ～パ！　甘やかしてぇ～！　パ～パっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "51.0",
      "line_index": 51,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ea0d7477",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "わ、わかった！　わかったから泣くなって……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "54.0",
      "line_index": 54,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4dba0da2",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "完全に赤ちゃんになりきってしまったイビリア。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "54.2",
      "line_index": 54,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "4dba0da2",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "とりあえず寝かしつけようとベッドの上にイビリアを寝かせる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "58.0",
      "line_index": 58,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ee3fb048",
      "speaker": "イビリア",
      "ja": "う～～っ！　あたち眠くない～っ！　まだ寝ない～っ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "61.0",
      "line_index": 61,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "96db3cc3",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "こら、暴れるなって。べ、別に寝なくてもいいから……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "61.2",
      "line_index": 61,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "96db3cc3",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "と、とりあえず落ち着こう？　な？　傍にいてあげるから",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "65.0",
      "line_index": 65,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9e907abc",
      "speaker": "イビリア",
      "ja": "ううー……！　それじゃつまんない～っ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "65.2",
      "line_index": 65,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "9e907abc",
      "speaker": "イビリア",
      "ja": "遊ぶのっ！　パパといっぱい遊ぶのーっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "68.0",
      "line_index": 68,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "679133c4",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（本当にどうしたらいいんだ……毎日毎日甘えてきて……。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "68.2",
      "line_index": 68,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "679133c4",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "何か根本的な解決方法はないのか……？　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "68.4",
      "line_index": 68,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "679133c4",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "毎日これじゃさすがに……ん？）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "71.0",
      "line_index": 71,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "242a7b54",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ふとイビリアの下半身に視線が向いてしまい、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "71.2",
      "line_index": 71,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "242a7b54",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "思わず釘付けになってしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "74.0",
      "line_index": 74,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2f039f9f",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（心は赤ちゃんになりきっていても身体は大人なんだよな……。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "74.2",
      "line_index": 74,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "2f039f9f",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "あのオムツの下にはイビリアのあそこが……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "78.0",
      "line_index": 78,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8b393419",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（うう……何だかムラムラしてきた……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "83.0",
      "line_index": 83,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "73e02f5a",
      "speaker": "イビリア",
      "ja": "パパ～♥　あそぼっ？♥　あそぼっ？♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "86.0",
      "line_index": 86,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a73a1c3b",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "あ、ああ……そう、だな……。でもその前に……ちっちしなきゃいけないよ……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "91.0",
      "line_index": 91,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e5539655",
      "speaker": "イビリア",
      "ja": "ふぇ？　パパ……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "93.0",
      "line_index": 93,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "981e5413",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "イビリアの髪をそっと撫で、そして服をするすると脱がす。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "94.0",
      "line_index": 94,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "feed19e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "大きな胸が飛び出るように露になり、それがさらに俺を興奮へと誘う。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "97.0",
      "line_index": 97,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2446505b",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "いっぱい遊んであげるから……大人しくしているんだよ？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "100.0",
      "line_index": 100,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f4a571d8",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "俺は優しくイビリアにそう伝えると、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "100.2",
      "line_index": 100,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "f4a571d8",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "興奮に任せるままにイビリアのオムツの中に手を入れた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "114.0",
      "line_index": 114,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1b5fccbf",
      "speaker": "イビリア",
      "ja": "ふああっ！？♥　パパ……あ、あああ……！♥　指ぃ……はううっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "116.0",
      "line_index": 116,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3004ace5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "オムツの中に手を入れられ、驚きの声をあげるイビリア。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "117.0",
      "line_index": 117,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2e8e3e81",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "しかし俺の予想とは違い、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "117.2",
      "line_index": 117,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "2e8e3e81",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "イビリアのあそこはすでに愛液でドロドロに溢れていた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "120.0",
      "line_index": 120,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "20f577a8",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "オムツの中でエッチなお漏らししているなんて……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "120.2",
      "line_index": 120,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "20f577a8",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "最初から期待していたんだな？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "124.0",
      "line_index": 124,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3e6db0bb",
      "speaker": "イビリア",
      "ja": "う～♥　そんなことにゃいもん……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "124.2",
      "line_index": 124,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "3e6db0bb",
      "speaker": "イビリア",
      "ja": "あたちそんなにエッチな娘じゃ……はうっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "129.0",
      "line_index": 129,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e434e8c6",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "指をそっと膣穴に差し込むと腰を大きく跳ねらせる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "130.0",
      "line_index": 130,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6f68de52",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "くちゅくちゅと膣穴を拡げるように指を動かすと、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "130.2",
      "line_index": 130,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "6f68de52",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "頬が赤くなり始め額からは汗が滴っていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "133.0",
      "line_index": 133,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d7061ea0",
      "speaker": "イビリア",
      "ja": "パパ……くちゅくちゅ……らめぇ♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "133.2",
      "line_index": 133,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "d7061ea0",
      "speaker": "イビリア",
      "ja": "んっ♥　んっ……♥　ふううう……！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "135.0",
      "line_index": 135,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c82d9295",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "おしゃぶりを咥えながら必死に快感に耐える。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "136.0",
      "line_index": 136,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4969e838",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "表情がどんどんいやらしくなり始め、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "136.2",
      "line_index": 136,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "4969e838",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それが俺を余計に興奮させていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "139.0",
      "line_index": 139,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "25b3e9e8",
      "speaker": "イビリア",
      "ja": "パパっ……ダメ……ダメだってぇ……んぅ♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "139.2",
      "line_index": 139,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "25b3e9e8",
      "speaker": "イビリア",
      "ja": "おまんまん、感じて……あうっ！♥ パパの指……気持ち、良い……♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "139.4",
      "line_index": 139,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "25b3e9e8",
      "speaker": "イビリア",
      "ja": "んぅ……ふっ♥　ふうううっ……！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "141.0",
      "line_index": 141,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d79b2bed",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "膣中はきゅっと指を締め上げ、奥から新鮮な愛液が噴水のように溢れる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "143.0",
      "line_index": 143,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "130eac25",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "快感に耐えきれないのか、逃げるように腰を揺するが、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "143.2",
      "line_index": 143,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "130eac25",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そっと脚を掴むと、さらに激しく指を膣穴に押し込んでいく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "146.0",
      "line_index": 146,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a8ee5cff",
      "speaker": "イビリア",
      "ja": "パパぁっ……♥　ダメ、だってぇ……もう許してぇ……♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "146.2",
      "line_index": 146,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "a8ee5cff",
      "speaker": "イビリア",
      "ja": "わ、わがまま、言わないからぁ……んぅぅぅ！♥　ふ、ふううう……！！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "149.0",
      "line_index": 149,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3e0875ad",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "でも中途半端で止めるのは嫌だろう？　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "149.2",
      "line_index": 149,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "3e0875ad",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "最後までして、スッキリすればよく眠れるようになるから",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "153.0",
      "line_index": 153,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "25bae9de",
      "speaker": "イビリア",
      "ja": "ううううっ！♥　んんぅぅぅっ！♥　はうっ！？　そ、そこ……んんっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "155.0",
      "line_index": 155,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "25150c69",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "指がＧスポットに触れると、イビリアは目を見開きこちらを見る。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "156.0",
      "line_index": 156,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8572968c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "首をぶんぶんと横に振り、その様子から絶頂が近いことを悟る。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "159.0",
      "line_index": 159,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4e39566f",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ほら、大人しくして。エッチなイビリアのオマンコイかせてあげるから",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "163.0",
      "line_index": 163,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7997694c",
      "speaker": "イビリア",
      "ja": "ふっ♥　ふうう……♥　パパ、らめ……らめぇ……！♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "163.2",
      "line_index": 163,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "7997694c",
      "speaker": "イビリア",
      "ja": "おまんまん……イっ、ちゃうぅ！♥　んんっ！♥　ううううっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "166.0",
      "line_index": 166,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2dedfa63",
      "speaker": "イビリア",
      "ja": "パパ……！！♥　う、う、うっ！♥　ふ、んぅ、んんんんんっ！！♥♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "197.0",
      "line_index": 197,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7b16698",
      "speaker": "イビリア",
      "ja": "ふあっ！♥　んんっ！♥　ふあああぁぁぁぁぁんっ！！♥♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "199.0",
      "line_index": 199,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "10c2ea8f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "可愛い悲鳴とともに、イビリアは全身をガクガクと痙攣させる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "201.0",
      "line_index": 201,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b087fe41",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "蕩けた表情を晒しながら、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "201.2",
      "line_index": 201,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "b087fe41",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "おしゃぶりをするのも忘れるほど何度も甘い悲鳴を口から漏らす。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "204.0",
      "line_index": 204,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2df1e599",
      "speaker": "イビリア",
      "ja": "う、あ……ダメ……♥　う、うう……出、ちゃ……♥　あああ……！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "207.0",
      "line_index": 207,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "db903ad4",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ん……？　何だか暖かい……これ……",
